text: Henry Fortescue (by 1515 – 1576), of Faulkbourne, Essex, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Maldon in March 1553 and for Sudbury in 1559, and High Sheriff of Essex in 1553. ==References== Category:1576 deaths Category:People from Braintree District Category:Year of birth uncertain Category:Members of Parliament for Maldon Henry Category:English MPs 1553 (Edward VI) Category:English MPs 1559
